<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5504067003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Check that the following condition is satisfied in this procedure.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
11 V &#60; Battery voltage &#60; 15 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ON for 10 sec. in P or N range.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5504067004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENBP70A5504067005">
<testgroup id = "AENBP70A5504067006">
<question>
Was “CVT System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A5504001">CVT System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70A5504067007">
<title>
ROM communication circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
With ignition OFF, disconnect “C142”, “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “C142”, “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “A1”, “A2” and “A3” circuits: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between each of “A1”, “A2” and “A3” circuits and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between each of “A1”, “A2” and “A3” circuit terminals and other terminal at “C142” connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage of “A1”, “A2” and “A3” circuits: approx. 0 V (when ignition is ON)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70A5504067008">
<title>
DTC recheck
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A5506001">TCM Learning Value Initialization</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Clear DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5504012"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform DTC confirmation procedure and check DTC.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is DTC P1826 still detected?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<paragroup>
<ptxt>
If DTC P1826 is still detected, replace CVT assembly and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5506019"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If DTC other than P1826 is detected, go to troubleshooting for applicable DTC.
</ptxt>
</paragroup>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Intermittent trouble.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
